name: Ni Chuba Na??
Lore: '''Your buddy here was about to be turned into orange goo. He picked a fight with a Dug. An especially dangerous Dug called Sebulba.''',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Once per turn may use 1 Force to look through opponent''s Lost Pile and place all docking bays you find there out of play. Once per game may deploy Sebulba from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. (Immune to Alter.)',
